<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Thank you for using TravelManager! This privacy policy explains how we handle the personal information you provide when using our application.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>As a student project, TravelManager may collect the following types of information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Basic account details: Your name, email address, and password (for creating and managing your account).</li>
    <li>Optional information: If you provide feedback, suggestions, or contact us, we may collect additional information.</li>
    <li>Non-personal data: General usage statistics, such as the number of users or visits to the site.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Why We Collect Your Information</h2>
<p>We collect this information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Enable basic functionality, like account registration and login.</li>
    <li>Improve the application as part of the learning experience.</li>
    <li>Test features and gather user feedback to enhance functionality.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How Your Information Is Protected</h2>
<p>As a student project, we take basic precautions to protect your information, including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Storing data securely using password hashing for accounts.</li>
    <li>Limiting access to sensitive information.</li>
</ul>
<p>However, as this is not a commercial-grade application, we recommend avoiding the use of sensitive or critical personal information.</p>

<h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>TravelManager does not share your personal information with third parties. Your data is solely used within the context of this student project.</p>

<h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
<p>This application may use basic cookies to enhance the user experience (e.g., saving session data). No advanced tracking mechanisms are implemented.</p>

<h2>6. Contact Information</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact the project owner or supervisor directly.</p>
